你听起来就好像是我爸爸

383
00:32:28,780 --> 00:32:33,313
I really don t care for the way you re speaking to

384
00:32:33,314 --> 00:32:37,287
me. It seems as if you were my father.

385
00:32:37,287 --> 00:32:41,620
表示与过去事实相反 谓语用过去完成时

386
00:32:41,620 --> 00:32:45,460
It seems as if he has been to America.

387
00:32:45,461 --> 00:32:47,554
他好像去过美国

388
00:32:47,554 --> 00:32:51,407
