438
00:36:17,963 --> 00:36:21,657
她说她希望他明天走 而不是今天

439
00:36:21,657 --> 00:36:26,323
She says she d rather he left tomorrow instead of today.

440
00:36:26,323 --> 00:36:29,097
would rather sb. had done

441
00:36:29,097 --> 00:36:30,443
